/thu_ke_tay/loai/chim%20canh%20cut.jpg">- H&igrave;nh chim c&aacute;nh cụt</a><br />\r\n	- <a href="/static/team/upload/images/2012/thu_ke_tay/loai/chuot%20cuoi.jpg">H&igrave;nh chuột</a><br />\r\n	- H&igrave;nh <a href="/static/team/upload/images/2012/thu_ke_tay/loai/Cop%20nam%20ngua.jpg">cọp nằm ngửa</a>, <a href="/static/team/upload/images/2012/thu_ke_tay/loai/cop%20nam%20sap.jpg">cọp nằm sấp</a><br />\r\n	- H&igrave;nh <a href="/static/team/upload/images/2012/thu_ke_tay/loai/Gau%20nam%20ngua.jpg">gấu nằm ngửa</a>, <a href="/static/team/upload/images/2012/thu_ke_tay/loai/gau%20nap%20sap.jpg">gấu nằm sấp</a><br />\r\n	- H&igrave;nh <a href="/static/team/upload/images/2012/thu_ke_tay/loai/Heo%20doi%20non.jpg">heo đội n&oacute;n</a>, <a href="/static/team/upload/images/2012/thu_ke_tay/loai/Heo%20mat%20kieng.jpg">heo mắt k&iacute;nh</a>, <a href="/static/team/upload/images/2012/thu_ke_tay/loai/heo%20mui%20to.jpg">heo mũi bự</a>, <a href="/static/team/upload/images/2012/thu_ke_tay/loai/heo%20nam%20ngua.jpg">heo nằm ngửa</a>, <a href="/static/team/upload/images/2012/thu_ke_tay/loai/heo%20tai%20dai.jpg">heo cười tai d&agrave;i</a><br />\r\n	- <a href="/static/team/upload/images/2012/thu_ke_tay/loai/Huu%20sung.jpg">H&igrave;nh hưu cười</a><br />\r\n	- <a href="/static/team/upload/images/2012/thu_ke_tay/loai/ngua%20cuoi.jpg">H&igrave;nh ngựa cười</a><br />\r\n	- <a href="/static/team/upload/images/2012/thu_ke_tay/loai/Khi.jpg">H&igrave;nh khỉ cười</a><br />\r\n	- <a href="/static/team/upload/images/2012/thu_ke_tay/loai/meo-kitty.jpg">H&igrave;nh m&egrave;o kitty</a><br />\r\n	- <a href="/static/team/upload/images/2012/thu_ke_tay/loai/tho%20tai%20tron.jpg">H&igrave;nh thỏ tai tr&ograve;n</a><br />\r\n	- H&igrave;nh <a href="/static/team/upload/images/2012/thu_ke_tay/loai/trau%20cuoi.jpg">tr&acirc;u cười</a>, <a href="/static/team/upload/images/2012/thu_ke_tay/loai/bo%20deo%20no.jpg">b&ograve; đeo nơ</a></span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><